《'''遠方禁戀'''》（{{lang-es|'''''Desde allá'''''}}）是一部2015年[[洛伦佐·维加斯|洛伦佐·维加斯]]执导的[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]][[同性恋|同性恋]]剧情片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/topnews/2015/09/12/leone-doro-a-desde-alla-di-vigas_31d47e83-b089-4c8f-8d4d-8ac240b59c91.html|title=Leone d'oro a Desde Alla di Vigas|date=2015-09-12|publisher=ANSA|language=it|access-date=2015-09-12|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803004713/http://www.ansa.it/sito/notizie/topnews/2015/09/12/leone-doro-a-desde-alla-di-vigas_31d47e83-b089-4c8f-8d4d-8ac240b59c91.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="InComp">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2015-full-list-1201486791/|title=Venice Film Festival: Lido Lineup Builds Awards Season Buzz – Full List|accessdate=29 July 2015|work=Deadline|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808192428/http://deadline.com/2015/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2015-full-list-1201486791/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/venice-fest-reveals-robust-lineup-featuring-hollywood-stars-and-international-auteurs-1201551960/|title=Venice Fest Reveals Robust Lineup Featuring Hollywood Stars and International Auteurs|accessdate=29 July 2015|work=Variety|archive-date=2017-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170625075544/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/venice-fest-reveals-robust-lineup-featuring-hollywood-stars-and-international-auteurs-1201551960/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，赢得[[第72届威尼斯影展|第72届威尼斯影展]][[金狮奖|金狮奖]]，这是首部入围威尼斯影展的委内瑞拉电影，也是继[[李安|李安]]的《[[断背山|断背山]]》后，又一部夺得金狮奖的同志题材电影<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0913/05/B3CD32FI00031H2L.html |language= |title=《来自远方》爆冷夺金狮 《断背山》获奖十年后 |publisher=网易娱乐 |date=2015-09-13 |accessdate= |archive-date=2015-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918003246/http://ent.163.com/15/0913/05/B3CD32FI00031H2L.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。代表委内瑞拉角逐[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳外語片角逐名單|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳外語片]]。

== 剧情 ==
讲述一位中年富有男人与一名街头[[黑帮|黑帮]]青年之间的同性关系。<ref name="BBC">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-34236541 |title=Venezuelan film Desde Alla wins top Venice festival award |accessdate=13 September 2015 |work=BBC News |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108102555/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-34236541 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HWR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/afar-desde-alla-venice-review-821716 |title='From Afar' ('Desde alla'): Venice Review |accessdate=13 September 2015 |work=Hollywood Reporter |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127174654/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/afar-desde-alla-venice-review-821716 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

